   3    1    2    p2 -> 3 3 2 -> p3 -> 3 3 5 -> p1 -> 5 3 5
   2    3    0    p3 -> 2 3 3 -> p1 -> 4 3 3 -> p2 -> 4 5 3
   3    3    0    p3 -> 3 3 3 -> p2 -> 3 5 3 -> p1 -> 5 5 3 